            "title": "美股日誌｜ 憧憬美伊談判　3大指數向好",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"美股日誌｜ 憧憬美伊談判 3大指數向好\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/hEKEMlWd7P3D9p0srIeFTA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/436d0330-2892-11f1-acfa-13243cb175f2\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">美股日誌｜ 憧憬美伊談判 3大指數向好</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國股市周三上升，投資者評估有報道指美國已向伊朗提出停火方案，市場對這場動盪市場的戰事可能降溫抱持審慎樂觀態度。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">標普500指數上升0.5%；道指上升約0.6%；以科技股為主的納斯達克綜合指數上升約0.7%，扭轉華爾街前一交易日的跌勢。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">油價回落，延續劇烈波動。布蘭特原油期貨則回落至每桶 97 美元以下。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"1\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"下載Yahoo財經APP\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:下載Yahoo財經APP;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://mobile.yahoo.com/finance?pid=editorial&amp;c=HK_Acquisition_YMktg_Evergreen_article_&amp;af_sub1=Acquisition&amp;af_sub2=HK_YMktg&amp;af_sub4=1058&amp;af_sub5=article__Banner_&amp;uuid=eDFkEhESdIhPGYRE2850\"><ins>下載Yahoo財經APP</ins></a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美股外幣即時報價 多國新聞任睇<br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">3月25日（星期三）市况</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"2\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"道瓊斯指數\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:道瓊斯指數;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EDJI\"><ins> 道瓊斯指數</ins></a> 升305.43點或0.66%，報46,429.49點。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-34dbae6a-4cc1-4a10-8c87-120b7679cdf8-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:3;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"3\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"標普500指數\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:標普500指數;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EGSPC\"><ins> 標普500指數</ins></a> 升35.53點或0.54%，報6,591.9點。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:4;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"4\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"納斯達克指數\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:納斯達克指數;cpos:4;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EIXIC\"><ins> 納斯達克指數</ins></a> 升167.93點或0.77%，報21,929.83點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:5;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"5\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"紐約5月期油\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:紐約5月期油;cpos:5;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/CL=F\"><ins> 紐約5月期油</ins></a> 收報91.29美元一桶，跌1.06美元或1.15%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:6;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"6\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"紐約4月期金\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:紐約4月期金;cpos:6;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/GC=F\"><ins> 紐約4月期金</ins></a> 收報4,503.3美元一盎司，升101.3美元或2.3%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:7;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"7\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"比特幣\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:比特幣;cpos:7;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/BTC-USD/\"><ins> 比特幣</ins></a> 截至美東時間下午4時報70,849.5美元，升1,573.11美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:8;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"8\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"美國10年期國債息率\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:美國10年期國債息率;cpos:8;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5ETNX\"><ins> 美國10年期國債息率</ins></a> 收報4.328厘。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據美聯社引述巴基斯坦官員報道，伊朗收到一項包含15點內容的方案，旨在結束中東衝突。市場認為該提案反映特朗普政府希望遏止衝突升級的迫切性，因戰事可能對經濟造成嚴重衝擊。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管特朗普表示美國正與伊朗進行持續談判，但德黑蘭否認存在直接對話，並於周三表示已拒絕美國提出的方案。即使如此，相關消息仍帶動市場風險偏好略為回升，並推動市場對聯儲局今年減息的押注。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">外媒報道，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:9;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"9\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Meta\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:Meta;cpos:9;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/META/\">Meta</a>(META.US)計劃裁減數百個工作崗位，是次業務重組影響到多個團隊，包括銷售、招聘和Reality Labs硬件部門。 消息指這次裁員將影響美國及其他國際市場的員工，部分受影響的員工可能獲調任其他職位</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">(NVDA.US)股價升2%，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:10;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"10\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"AMD\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:AMD;cpos:10;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/AMD/\">AMD</a>(AMD.US)及<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:11;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"11\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"英特爾\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:英特爾;cpos:11;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/INTC/\">英特爾</a>(INTC.US)一同大升7%，是納指成分股最好表現的股份。<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:12;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"12\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"亞馬遜\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:亞馬遜;cpos:12;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/AMZN/\">亞馬遜</a>(AMZN.US)收購人形機械人開發商Fauna Robotics，股價升逾2%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">新股方面，馬斯克的火箭與衛星製造公司SpaceX考慮將IPO籌資目標定在史上最高水平，超過之前全球任何一家公司的募股規模。其中一名知情人士表示，SpaceX正在權衡將募資額定在約750億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這數字遠高於彭博此前報導的500億美元目標，比當前全球IPO記錄之最，亦即沙烏地阿美2019年290億美元上市規模，足足高出一倍有多。</p></div>",
